      "role": "user",
      "content": "that sounds like a good start but it feels a bit generic. i want to add more grit or conflict to the scene to make it more dramatic for the show. like, u know, things that are more characteristic of that community—maybe there’s more tension or certain types of arguments that happen regularly? give me some ideas for realistic conflict that would fit that setting.",
